<emphasis id="B944552CFFE10F45FA3EF2EDCA68F2CC" bold="true" box="[1454,1565,3410,3439]" pageId="19" pageNumber="202">Habitat.</emphasis>
Moist savannas and woodlands,typically above elevations of 500 m.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
